絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"915727185e0d4bd473c0da1974c5af7e300194e5","tid":1728770,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:31:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7889a7e655f2423fc598c44078624df701b65198","tid":1728770,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:32:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d581118791aa13b53cb9321f54b40162adf0bf16","tid":1728770,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"915727185e0d4bd473c0da1974c5af7e300194e5","tid":1728770,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b596dd8110550fe41f6a0a677bd722c806d110e","tid":1728770,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:13:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係連普通市民都轉風向屌柒政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:31:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:33:03.000Z","msg":"由佢地清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c94a0850a89c77629f41e024fa58e1abebbc02","tid":1728770,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/